- "compare in terms of the number of wines they produce" means the regions are ranked by the number of wines they have.

sql:
SELECT SUM(T1.price_inc_vat * T2.quantity) AS total_value
FROM prices T1
INNER JOIN inventory T2 ON T1.wine_id = T2.wine_id;

